{"tid":1627982,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"擺買三中商同叫人幫襯其他小型書店就夠","createTime":"2019-10-05T19:49:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T00:18:20.000Z","uid":311783,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f943255c371e2b2c768f284b218f58cc501c6f6a","tid":1627982,"uid":311783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T19:49:12.000Z","msg":"首先唔係反對裝修，<br />\n但如果搞著書店，<br />\n個觀感真係好差，<br />\n絕對會被對家話係紅衛兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n大家唔好忘記七一個陣，<br />\n我地唔破壞文物就已經顯示咗我地有別於紅衛兵。<br />\n<br />\n咁唔通有得班三中商繼續聾斷咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地應該不斷文宣三中商係中聯辦控制，<br />\n再提倡入三中商齋睇不買，<br />\n然後整張list係其他小書店貼係連儂牆推薦人去買。<br />\n<br />\n希望其他巴絲亦留低你地平日去開既書店，<br />\n我平日就會去開：<br />\n田園書屋<br />\n學津書店<br />\n梅馨書舍<br />\n見山書店"},{"pid":"f7e00725e7733842500d6ea2a4886885bab33a32","tid":1627982,"uid":241742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T20:17:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3564dc91856e22afb2c8b71b88cab205f5cf3c50","tid":1627982,"uid":268160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T20:18:34.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"fa23562c0abbfa02ae8a1af3759c00594b111595","tid":1627982,"uid":28818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T00:07:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[香港本土書店List]裝飾罷買三中商，中共思想控制香港人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1632803\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1632803</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cabd68c81665ef512fc8101fc194a2d88e990f2f","tid":1627982,"uid":298127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T00:09:12.000Z","msg":"樂文書店！"},{"pid":"232a68c675153bac29fea55972eb2d7caac0fb32","tid":1627982,"uid":124282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T00:18:20.000Z","msg":"推！"}]}